SUMMARY:Level Up Summit
DESCRIPTION:The Level Up Summit at Morgan State University is inviting our developer community to showcase games on Saturday\, April 25th! \nThe Level Up Summit is an event focused on collegiate Esports and gamer culture in Baltimore. We only have space for about 5 exhibitors\, so get your application in fast. Applications Close on April 10th. \nIf you would like to exhibit at this event\, please fill out this form: Level Up Summit Indie Exhibitor Application
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/level-up-summit/
END:VEVENT
